HDO Box / HDO Pro MOD

This repository is no longer the main home of the project.

Originally, this project was known as HDO Box MOD and focused on improving the user experience through modifications and optimizations such as:

* No Ads
* Faster Loading Times
* Reduced Interruptions
* Optimized Performance

As the project grew, it eventually evolved into its own community-driven project and was later rebranded as HDO Pro.

This repository represents an older stage of the project before the HDO Pro community rebrand and transition into an independent community project.

Development is no longer maintained here.

Current repository:
https://github.com/HDO-PRO/hdo-pro

Note:
This repository is kept online for archival and historical purposes only. Updates, announcements, and future development take place in the current repository.

Thank you to everyone who supported the project throughout its journey from HDO Box to HDO Pro.
